column2: plot_data <- obss %>% gather(name, data,-Date) %>% arrange(Date) %>% ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x =Date, y=data, color=name)) + facet_wrap(~name, scale="free_y") + ggthemes::scale_color_wsj() + labs(y = "Data", x = "Date", title = "Observable Data Series", subtitle= "Quarterly changes from 1982 to 2019", caption = "Source: fred.stlouisfed.org") + theme(legend.position="non")
